tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits. Glycemic control (HbA1c, glucose) is adequate, and renal function (urea, creatinine) is normal. Electrolytes and calcium are also within reference ranges. No laboratory abnormalities detected at this time. Recommend routine follow-up as clinically indicated.
